Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:21.56,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Forever... Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.74,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,The first day I touched you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:30.12,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,my heart pounded so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:33.63,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I decided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:37.76,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,in my heart to follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.54,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of the flowers and wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.76,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,the smell of this soup...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:49.95,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if they disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:53.85,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,as long as I can be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:03:09.86,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I could hear the sound \Nof this tiny hope growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:10.41,Title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1399,1)}A New Journey
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:14.14,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear the song of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.66,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Minori could've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,She's working at Karashin's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:23.30,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Minori is a working lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,"A working lady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:27.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something people normally say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:37.93,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isuzu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.27,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.68,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.09,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.45,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm full of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.32,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.08,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,That was really amazing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.84,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,You really seemed like a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.32,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:56.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The owner was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.98,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,He looked like he was glad \Nhe asked you to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:01.09,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound like such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.77,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's basically a once-a-week part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.39,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,And the song was just a cover of \Nsomething I heard a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.75,0:04:10.75,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone looked truly happy listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.73,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:16.24,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isuzu is such a great artist, \Nshe must have a muse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:17.83,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.94,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:23.99,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I just know a little bit because I've always had \Ninstruments in my house since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.88,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Your sweet melodies bring life \Nto the city streets at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:32.50,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,and your dazzling voice brings peace to \Nthe hearts of even birds and beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:36.97,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Rudy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:41.28,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with saying it was great, \Nwhen it was great?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.72,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.10,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.40,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:48.72,Knights,,0000,0000,0000,,First Order of Knights of the People of the Land\NDrill Guidelines
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I plan to send Tohya and \Nthe other new members on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like Serara to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.82,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If she's okay with it, that's just fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.81,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But what quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,A magic bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Dazaneg's Magic Bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:12.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to get the materials for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:16.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, "Get the Magic Bag," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:18.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The one where you hunt the mini-wyverns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:23.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They've reached the minimum \Nlevel required for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.26,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They're already above level 45.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:34.39,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya seems to want to go. \NHe keeps bringing it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they want one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's convenient, since it holds everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:48.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think they actually want to try \Na real quest, all by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:53.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But will they be okay on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.53,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.81,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:02.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done working at Karashin's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.12,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great timing, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:28.73,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone complimented me, \Nbut I'm not that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.74,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:36.55,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,No one ever told me my music was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:39.46,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,But no one ever told me it was good, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:44.36,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I can't be a pro like you, Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.55,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,I can at least play the lute once in a \Nwhile to blow off steam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.09,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.73,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,It makes everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you grinning like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:02.75,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... I was grinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:07.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:10.95,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You still feel great after that concert, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.45,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.72,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:20.55,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined myself on \Nthe stage, playing drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.20,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You were really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.71,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, bards are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:33.09,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You have an aura that makes even someone \Nlike me able to play, just by being near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:38.01,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, it seems you need \Nmusical sense for it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.10,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I tried asking Rudy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.95,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,How's this, Miss Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.00,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.61,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.11,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God! My hand's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:56.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But that just means you have \Nreally good musical sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:58.38,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.51,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I've just been used to music \Never since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:02.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I played soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:07.56,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but I was no match for the guys \Nwho were really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.58,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell when someone's a natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.79,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you're a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:21.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I sucked, it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.81,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You have fun playing music, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.75,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:30.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You like it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.28,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:34.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And you get to keep doing it, so it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:46.16,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what happened just \Nafter we were saved from Hamelin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:51.93,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed with the Crescent \NMoon Alliance for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.80,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,but you two had already decided \Nto come to this guild, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:04.31,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But I was suddenly free, \Nand I had no idea what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.82,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,And then I found this lute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:16.32,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,With the dolphin pattern lacquered on... \NIt was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:20.79,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was something Marielle \Nhad made long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked her to let me have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:29.46,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,And then I made a bunch of adjustments,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:33.84,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,and now it's my own personal instrument, \Nthe Flying Dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.74,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.20,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It gave me the drive to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:44.47,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy I can keep playing music.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:49.69,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.84,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:53.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.23,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya! Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.49,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe wants to talk to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,An adventure! A quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:13.02,Map,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Mt. Fuji                                                    Akihabara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:14.64,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,The Redstone Mountains are near Nagano, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:16.51,Map,T,0000,0000,0000,,Redstone Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.51,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mountains, rivers, forests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:19.26,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,And villages we've never been to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:23.30,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, stop staring at the map, \Nand pack two more pairs of underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's no room for all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:29.27,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have our magic bags yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:34.31,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know about traveling, \Nask me, Rundel Haus Code.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:38.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you used to travel alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:38.98,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.63,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Until partway, I was with other adventurers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.33,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,but I came all the way from Bogport \Nto Akihabara on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.47,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,So I have plenty of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:47.91,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.94,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.19,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,My very important brush is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:56.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't maintain my appearance \Nas an adventurer without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:59.10,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,My elegant, flowing hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.53,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.04,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:04.90,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's in your toiletries set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.07,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.93,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.15,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, clean all this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You guys ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.73,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,We're in perfect shape, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:19.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:22.18,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Put a barrel of water on the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.32,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.55,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,Making progress, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When did you get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.29,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You little—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:37.77,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,If you want any advice from me, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.87,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idol who travels the whole galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.95,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Naotsugu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.38,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,You know you love it—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.72,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.87,0:11:58.18,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,What's with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.77,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,They're worried about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:04.43,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,They really care about us a lot, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:06.90,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone always looks out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:11.65,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but they try not to let \Nus know they're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:19.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of tiring, knowing they're \Nlooking out for us all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.34,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to bet on who comes next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.12,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.67,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be Shiroe—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:28.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Preparations going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.18,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:34.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.90,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:40.53,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think we'll be done packing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.03,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll split up and go shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.53,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,pick up a carriage and weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:48.50,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta's going to come and \Nhelp us choose a carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I made this. It's a little more detailed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:03.47,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's finish here and go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:04.36,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.93,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop staring at the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.94,SignA,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H222B34&\3c&H759496&}Amenoma
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:18.94,Default,Ta,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.20,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Once we have weapons, then we'll need armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.95,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to make a few more stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:33.05,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell you're a samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.04,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,You look great with a katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:38.49,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to take this opportunity \Nto get a new one,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:42.46,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,but at my level, there aren't \Ntoo many I can use...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:46.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How about caltrop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:50.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think trying a ninja's \Nweapon would be interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki brought me along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You could go with shurikens, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:03.72,Default,Ta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, shurikens are a choice for a ranged weapon \Nthat can be used regardless of class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kunai are valuable ones, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.99,Default,Ta,0000,0000,0000,,I'd recommend the ones on the wall there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.40,Default,Ta,0000,0000,0000,,They're easy to use in a variety of situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:10.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.74,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no matter how good your weapon is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.69,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,in the end, it's all about your heart and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:20.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! When the time comes, a man \Nneeds to put his body on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.00,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:28.51,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And when even that's not enough, \Nremember this! Pant—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.52,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.52,Flutes,All,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not blow the flutes inside the store!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.48,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,These flutes are the ones that summon horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.28,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, look at all the animals you can summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.02,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Everything from dangerous beasts to pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:53.28,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Ew! You can summon rats and snakes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:56.78,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,What about the griffon? The one Shiroe has?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:15:01.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You need to do a special quest to get those,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,for things like a griffon or pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.11,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,A pegasus, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.25,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I want a pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.05,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,If I could ride on one with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:15.07,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,A pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:16.08,Default - italics,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:20.44,Default - italics,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I risked my life on a quest to get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.94,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,You're so wonderful, Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.98,Default - italics,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ride it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.57,Default - italics,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:29.05,Default - italics,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.07,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.83,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.44,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,There are actually a lot of different \Ntypes of carriages, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.20,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.05,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,This one looks really tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:53.21,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It has fire, cold, and electricity \Nresistances at rank 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.80,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.56,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's expensive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:05.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.48,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see the next one, Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.28,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of weird-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.85,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the people who make \Nthese are quite hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.11,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.82,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,This gorgeous, fit-for-a-celeb feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:33.55,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly the perfect carriage for me, \Na noble and great adventurer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.76,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though it was made just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:41.39,Default - italics,I,0000,0000,0000,,This doggy is all screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:51.65,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this looks like a reasonable choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.91,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:58.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You have excellent taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple, but the chassis and suspension \Nare made in an interesting way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:06.26,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's lightweight but tough, and the gyration \Nradius of the front wheels—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:08.92,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's expensive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.92,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the negotiations to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:17.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta showed me this great ramen place...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.32,0:17:20.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:21.43,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.98,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Does that taste good, Danish? Croissant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.21,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Those names sound like something \NSerara would think up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.98,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Want to give them cabbage, too, Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.91,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.80,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.39,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,That is no longer amusing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:55.55,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Just so we're clear, I'm a pro at handling horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.75,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:18:00.54,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,They're our companions from now on, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.99,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you shouldn't \Nscream like that, Miss Isuzu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.56,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Horses are easy to spook.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.71,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.32,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.94,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.95,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You apologize, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:18.81,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.32,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.95,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, horsey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.19,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:25.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:29.82,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.17,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.92,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw a picture to finish it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:38.22,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a giraffe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:49.23,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's dinner was specially made by Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.58,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta taught me how to cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:54.47,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll do the cooking on our journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:58.98,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in that Newlywed's Apron Dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:03.89,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I tried it, too, but when you wear it, \Nyou really look like a newlywed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.62,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:10.19,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Newlywed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.76,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:17.13,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.63,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:20.98,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.95,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I was feeling kind of bad that I couldn't eat
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta's cooking while we were on our trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.73,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this'll do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:37.11,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, isn't it kind of a shame for you, Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.11,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:43.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,During the trip, you won't be \Nable to play your concerts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:47.12,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but the trip itself is like a tour, so it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,A tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.25,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's when a musician goes on a trip to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.75,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I can go "dum da-da dum" on the carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.06,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! A tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.04,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We can do performances as we travel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:01.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.09,Default,Te,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice! A tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:08.30,Default - italics,Te,0000,0000,0000,,A touring trip around the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:11.99,Default - italics,Te,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the galactic idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:11.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're going beyond Izu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.99,0:20:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone join in with me, Tetra!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.74,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,A tour, huh? Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.21,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go around to villages, \Ndoing the forty-two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.66,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Forty-two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:23.84,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there are that \Nmany villages on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.87,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,No, the forty-two is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.31,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,There are about four or five villages
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between here and the Redstone Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.03,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's visit the villages and perform!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.33,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to visit them for \Nwater and stuff, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.67,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, isn't it, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:42.47,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.18,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get too out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens, contact us—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.31,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, if you can, I think you should avoid telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.83,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:58.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about things and solve them \Nyourselves, as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:02.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Journeys like this are a good chance to learn that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:06.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Go and see a lot of different worlds, \Nand enjoy a lot of different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:08.61,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:11.73,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to be your guide and lead this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:12.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.18,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,A tour is also a valuable experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.89,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Isuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.21,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.47,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.97,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.22,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stock up on spare strings!
